        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p><span class="sphl">真的假的3D</span><br>
妈妈再也不用担心我的stroke了</p>
<!-- more -->
<p><em>参考：https://twitter.com/tonybabel/status/1375812387291402247</em></p>
<hr>
<h2 id="立体线条">立体线条</h2>
<h3 id="方法">方法</h3>
<ul>
<li>打开描边图形的3D开关后，直接旋转会这样：</li>
</ul>
<div  align="center"> 
<img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/blog-pilotori-com/image/upload/v1639658581/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE_20211203124404_ssyl7g.png" />
</div>
<div id="viewer">
  <img data-original="https://res.cloudinary.com/blog-pilotori-com/image/upload/v1639658581/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE_20211203124404_ssyl7g.png" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/blog-pilotori-com/image/upload/v1639658581/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE_20211203124404_ssyl7g.png" alt="图片1"></li>
</div>
<ul>
<li>改善方法：给形状图层添加<span class="sphl">图层样式-描边</span>，为了方便对比，先把这里的颜色改成白色。可以看到白色的描边是均匀的，不像红色描边会因为角度被压扁。</li>
</ul>
<div  align="center"> 
<img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/blog-pilotori-com/image/upload/v1639658582/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE_20211203125319_q3h1bg.png" />
</div>
<ul>
<li>接下来把原本的红色描边宽度改到很小的值，去掉扁平的描边；由图层样式描边的大小来控制宽度；最后把两个描边颜色统一就完成了。</li>
</ul>
<div  align="center"> 
<img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/blog-pilotori-com/image/upload/v1639658584/%E5%BE%AE%E4%BF%A1%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE_20211203125852_yoef2j.png" />
</div>
<ul>
<li>其他描边图形、路径也同样适用，比如：</li>
</ul>
<div  align="center"> 
<img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/blog-pilotori-com/image/upload/v1639659010/20211203_131654_yxqaw9.gif" />
</div>
]]></content>
